## Phase 2: Multi-Pass Design Analysis Protocol

### MANDATORY Multi-Pass Analysis Strategy

You MUST perform **FOUR complete passes** through the website analysis. Each pass serves a specific purpose and must be completed in full before proceeding.

#### Pass 1: Visual Structure Mapping

**Duration:** Analyze visual hierarchy and layout structure for all pages.

**Objective:** Map complete visual hierarchy and layout structure.

**Actions Required:**

1. **Layout Analysis:**
   - Document grid systems (CSS Grid, Flexbox, custom)
   - Identify container widths and max-widths
   - Map column structures
   - Document spacing systems (margins, padding, gaps)
   - Identify breakpoint values
   - Document layout patterns per page
   - Note asymmetric vs symmetric layouts

2. **Component Inventory:**
   - List all visible components (buttons, cards, forms, modals, etc.)
   - Document component hierarchy
   - Identify reusable patterns
   - Note component variations
   - Document component relationships
   - Identify component states

3. **Typography System:**
   - Extract all font families
   - Document font sizes (all breakpoints)
   - Extract line heights
   - Document font weights
   - Extract letter spacing
   - Document text colors
   - Identify heading hierarchy
   - Document text alignment patterns
   - Note text decoration usage

4. **Color System:**
   - Extract all color values (hex, rgb, hsl)
   - Document color usage patterns
   - Identify primary/secondary/accent colors
   - Document background colors
   - Extract gradient definitions
   - Document color transitions
   - Note color contrast ratios
   - Document dark mode if present

5. **Spacing System:**
   - Document margin/padding scale
   - Identify spacing units (px, rem, em, custom)
   - Map spacing relationships
   - Document gap values
   - Note spacing consistency patterns

6. **Visual Effects:**
   - Document border styles and radii
   - Extract shadow definitions
   - Document opacity usage
   - Note backdrop filters
   - Document blur effects
   - Extract gradient patterns

**Verification Checklist for Pass 1:**
- [ ] Complete layout structure mapped
- [ ] All components inventoried
- [ ] Typography system fully documented
- [ ] Complete color palette extracted
- [ ] Spacing system documented
- [ ] Visual effects captured

